Follow the steps below to set up and run the Lightweight DeepFake Detection System locally.

1Ô∏è‚É£ Prerequisites

Make sure you have the following installed:

Python 3.11 (recommended)

pip (Python package manager)

Git (optional, for cloning)

Check Python version:

python --version

2Ô∏è‚É£ Clone the Repository
git clone https://github.com/your-username/Lightweight-DeepFake-Detection-Model.git
