Open your browser and visit:

http://127.0.0.1:7860

7Ô∏è‚É£ Use the Application

Upload an image (or video frame)

The system will classify it as:

REAL ‚úÖ

FAKE ‚ùå

UNCERTAIN ü§î (low confidence)

üß™ Notes

The UNCERTAIN output is intentional and represents low model confidence.

This project uses a lightweight CNN trained on a small dataset for demonstration.

Accuracy can be improved with larger datasets and transfer learning.

üõë Common Issues

ModuleNotFoundError ‚Üí Ensure virtual environment is activated

Model not found ‚Üí Run quick_train.py before inference

Always UNCERTAIN ‚Üí Model confidence is low due to limited training data
